\c 5
\s Vana vaAdhamu
\p
\v 1 Iri ibhuku renhoroondo yedzinza raAdhamu. Pazuva Mwari raakasika munhu, wakamuita nemufananidzo waMwari.
\v 2 Wakavasika murume nemukadzi, ndokuvaropafadza, akatumidza zita ravo \add kuti\add* munhu, pazuva ravakasikwa.
\v 3 Zvino Adhamu wakararama makore zana nemakumi matatu; ndokubereka \add mwanakomana\add* maererano nemufananidzo wake, wakamutodza; ndokutumidza zita rake Seti.
\v 4 Zvino mazuva aAdhamu shure kwekubereka Seti aiva makore mazana masere; ndokubereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\v 5 Zvino mazuva ose aAdhamu aakararama aiva makore mazana mapfumbamwe nemakumi matatu, ndokufa.
\p
\v 6 Zvino Seti wakararama makore zana nemashanu, ndokubereka Enosi.
\v 7 Seti ndokuraram abereka Enosi makore mazana masere nemanomwe; ndokubereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\v 8 Zvino ose mazuva aSeti aiva makore mazana mapfumbamwe negumi nemaviri; ndokufa.
\p
\v 9 Zvino Enosi wakararama makore makumi mapfumbamwe, ndokubereka Kenani.
\v 10 Zvino Enosi wakararama abereka Kenani makore mazana masere negumi nemashanu; ndokubereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\v 11 Zvino ose mazuva aEnosi aiva makore mazana mapfumbamwe nemashanu, ndokufa.
\p
\v 12 Zvino Kenani wakararama makore makumi manomwe, ndokubereka Maharareri.
\v 13 Kenani ndokurarama abereka Maharareri makore mazana masere nemakumi mana; ndokubereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\v 14 Nemazuva ose aKenani aiva makore mazana mapfumbamwe negumi, ndokufa.
\p
\v 15 Zvino Maharareri wakararama makore makumi matanhatu nemashanu, ndokubereka Jaredhi.
\v 16 Maharareri ndokuraramama abereka Jaredhi makore mazana masere nemakumi matatu; ndokubereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\v 17 Zvino ose mazuva aMaharareri aiva makore mazana masere nemakumi mapfumbamwe nemashanu; ndokufa.
\p
\v 18 Zvino Jaredhi wakararama makore zana nemakumi matanhatu nemaviri, ndokubereka Enoki.
\v 19 Jaredhi ndokurarama abereka Enoki makore mazana masere; ndokubereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\v 20 Zvino ose mazuva aJaredhi aiva makore mazana mapfumbamwe nemakumi matanhatu nemaviri; ndokufa.
\p
\v 21 Zvino Enoki wakararama makore makumi matanhatu nemashanu, ndokubereka Metusera.
\v 22 Zvino Enoki wakafamba naMwari abereka Metusera makore mazana matatu; ndokubereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\v 23 Nemazuva ose aEnoki aiva makore mazana matatu nemakumi matanhatu nemashanu.
\v 24 Enoki ndokufamba naMwari; uye haachipo, nekuti Mwari wakamutora.
\p
\v 25 Zvino Metusera wakararama makore zana nemakumi masere namanomwe, ndokubereka Rameki.
\v 26 Zvino Metusera wakararama abereka Rameki makore mazana manomwe namakumi masere namaviri; ndokubereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\v 27 Zvino mazuva ose aMetusera aiva makore mazana mapfumbamwe nemakumi matanhatu nemapfumbamwe, ndokufa.
\p
\v 28 Rameki ndokurarama makore zana nemakumi masere nemaviri; ndokubereka mwanakomana.
\v 29 Zvino wakamutumidza zita \add kuti\add* Nowa, achiti: Uyu achanyaradza pabasa redu nepakushingaira kwemaoko edu, nekuda kwepasi Jehovha paakatuka.
\v 30 Rameki akararama shure kwekubereka kwake Nowa, Rameki akagara makore ana mazana mashanu namakumi mapfumbamwe namashanu; akabereka vanakomana navanasikana.
\v 31 Nemazuva ose aRameki aiva makore mazana manomwe nemakumi manomwe nemanomwe, ndokufa.
\p
\v 32 Zvino Nowa waiva nemakore mazana mashanu, Nowa ndokubereka Shemu, naHamu, naJafeti.
